and Football League#Division One|1979\u201380]]\n}}\n\nDivision One featured 14 clubs which competed in the previous season, along with two new clubs:\n*[[Creswell Colliery F.C.|Creswell Colliery]], joined from the Sutton & Skegby League\n*[[Grantham F.C.|Grantham]] reserves\n\n\n===League table===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=LEG|name_LEG=[[Long Eaton Grange F.C.|Long Eaton Grange]]\n|team2=ARK|name_ARK=[[Arnold Kingswell F.C.|Arnold Kingswell]]\n|team3=OAK|name_OAK=[[Oakham United F.C. (Nottinghamshire)|Oakham United]]\n|team4=CRE|name_CRE=[[Creswell Colliery F.C.|Creswell Colliery]]\n|team5=LIN|name_LIN=[[Linby Colliery F.C.|Linby Colliery]]\n|team6=STA|name_STA=[[Staveley Works F.C.|Staveley Works]]\n|team7=GRA|name_GRA=[[Grantham F.C.|Grantham]] reserves\n|team8=LEU|name_LEU=[[Long Eaton United F.C.|Long Eaton United]] reserves\n|team9=ETR|name_ETR=[[Eastwood Town F.C.|Eastwood Town]] reserves\n|team10=ATT|name_ATT=[[Attenborough F.C.|Attenborough]]\n|team11=TIC|name_TIC=TI Chesterfield\n|team12=ARR|name_ARR=[[Arnold F.C.|Arnold]] reserves\n|team13=CAR|name_CAR=[[Carrvale United F.C.|Carrvale United]]\n|team14=CCW|name_CCW=[[Clay Cross Works F.C.|Clay Cross Works]]\n|team15=KIM|name_KIM=[[Kimberley Town F.C.|Kimberley Town]] reserves\n|team16=RIP|name_RIP=[[Ripley Town F.C.|Ripley Town]]\n\n|win_ARK=21|draw_ARK=4|loss_ARK=5|gf_ARK=79|ga_ARK=30\n|win_ARR=8|draw_ARR=9|loss_ARR=13|gf_ARR=32|ga_ARR=49\n|win_ATT=11|draw_ATT=4|loss_ATT=15|gf_ATT=45|ga_ATT=60\n|win_CAR=6|draw_CAR=8|loss_CAR=16|gf_CAR=27|ga_CAR=54\n|win_CCW=8|draw_CCW=5|loss_CCW=17|gf_CCW=27|ga_CCW=54\n|win_CRE=14|draw_CRE=10|loss_CRE=6|gf_CRE=53|ga_CRE=37\n|win_ETR=9|draw_ETR=8|loss_ETR=13|gf_ETR=45|ga_ETR=52\n|win_GRA=9|draw_GRA=12|loss_GRA=9|gf_GRA=40|ga_GRA=37\n|win_KIM=5|draw_KIM=9|loss_KIM=16|gf_KIM=34|ga_KIM=53\n|win_LEG=22|draw_LEG=4|loss_LEG=4|gf_LEG=51|ga_LEG=23\n|win_LEU=13|draw_LEU=2|loss_LEU=15|gf_LEU=43|ga_LEU=50\n|win_LIN=14|draw_LIN=