Jeremi\u0107]]|starter_pg = [[Jovan Novak]]|bench 1_c = [[Ljubomir \u010campara]]|bench 1_pf = [[Aleksandar Bursa\u0107]]|bench 1_sf = [[Milo\u0161 Grubor]]|bench 1_sg = [[Marko Radonji\u0107]]|bench 1_pg = [[Svetozar Popovi\u0107]]|bench 2_sg = [[Stevan Vrba\u0161ki]]|bench 2_sf = [[Marko Brankovi\u0107]]|bench 3_pf = [[Marko Radenovi\u0107]]|bench 3_sg = [[\u0110or\u0111e Cvjetan]]}}\n\n=== Left club during the season ===\n[[Stefan Pot]] ''(to [[CSU Asesoft Ploie\u0219ti]])''\n\n[[Bo\u017eo \u0110umi\u0107]] ''(to [[KK Partizan]])''\n\n=== Joined club during the season ===\n[[Jovan Novak]] ''(Free Agent)''\n\n[[Marko Radonji\u0107]] (''from [[KK Napredak Kru\u0161evac|Napredak Kru\u0161evac]])''\n\n== Statistics ==\n{{ACB player statistics legend}}\n\n=== Basketball league of Serbia ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Player\n!GP\n!MPG\n!FG%\n!3FG%\n!FT%\n!RPG\n!APG\n!SPG\n!BPG\n!PPG\n|-\n|[[Marko Brankovic|Marko Brankovi\u0107]]\n| 11\n| 12.3\n| 50%\n| 25%\n| 50%\n| 1.0\n| 0.5\n| 0.5\n| 0.0\n| 2.6\n|-\n|[[Aleksandar Bursac|Aleksandar Bursa\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Ljubomir Campara|Ljubomir \u010campara]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|\u0110or\u0111e [[Djordje Cvjetan|Cvjetan]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Bo\u017eo \u0110umi\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Milos Grubor]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Marko Jeremic|Marko Jeremi\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Nebojsa Jovisic|Neboj\u0161a Jovi\u0161i\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Stefan Matic|Stefan Mati\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Jovan Novak]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Svetozar Popovi\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Stefan Pot]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Milos Radenovic|Milo\u0161 Radenovi\u0107]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Rado\u0161 \u0160e\u0161lija]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|-\n|[[Stevan Vrba\u0161ki]]\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:2014-15 KK Vojvodina Srbijagas season}}\n[[Category:2014\u201315 in Serbian basketball by club|Vojvodina]]\n", "text_old": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{Orphan|date=June 2016}}\n{{unreferenced|date=May 2016}}\n}}\n\nIn 2014\u201315 season the club competed in both parts of [[Basketball League of Serbia]] and [[Radivoj Kora\u0107 Cup]].\n\n== Basketball league of Serbia ==\n{{Infobox basketball club season\n| club               = KK Vojvodina Srbijagas\n| season             = 2014\u201315 \n| manager            = Dusan Alimpijievic \n| stadium            = SPC Vojvodina\n| league             = Basketball League of Serbia\n| league result      = 3rd\n| league2            = Basketball League of Serbia\n| league2 result     = 5th\n| cup1               = Radivoj Kora\u0107 Cup\n| cup1 result        = Quarter-final\n| h_body        = FFFFFF\n| h_pattern_b   = _redhalf\n| h_shorts      = FFFFFF\n| h_pattern_s   = \n| a_body        = 082567\n| a_pattern_b   = _thinredsides\n| a_shorts      = 082567\n| a_pattern_s   = \n| 3_body        = \n| 3_pattern_b   = \n| 3_shorts      = \n| 3_pattern_s   = \n| prevseason = 2013\u201314\n| nextseason = 2015\u201316\n}}The club began the season without any high ambitions and they surprised many people after winning the first 10 games, before losing to [[OKK Beograd]] in the 11th round. During the season two leading players [[Stefan Pot]] and [[Bo\u017eo \u0110umi\u0107]] left the club. They still managed to bring in the young and talent [[Jovan Novak]] who quickly became one of the best players in the league. [[KK Vojvodina Srbijagas|Vojvodina]] finished the season with 17 victories and 5 loses on the 3rd place.\n\n== Serbian Superleague ==\nIn the second part of the season [[KK Vojvodina Srbijagas|Vojvodina]] continued to go strong and won 3 games in a row following the 1st round loss against [[KK Metalac Valjevo|Metalac Valjevo]], before losing to [[KK Partizan|Partizan]] at home. They finished the season in the 5th place with the score 6-8.\n\n== Players ==\n{{Basketball roster header|color1 = White|Color2 = Red|bg1 = Red|bg 2 = Blue|team = KK Vojvodina Srbijagas}}\n\n<!-- list of players -->\n{{Player3|num = 4|first = Neboj\u0161a|last = Jovi\u0161i\u0107|nat = SER|m = 2.00|pos = PF|year = 1988|month = 4|date = 29}}{{Player3|num = 5|first = Jovan|last = Novak|m = 1.88|pos = PG|nat = SER|year = 1994|month = 11|date = 8}}{{Player3|num = 6|first = Stevan|last = Vrba\u0161ki|pos = SG|m = 1.96|nat = SER}}{{Player3|num = 7|first = Ljubomir|last = \u010campara|pos = PF|nat = SER|m = 2.03|year = 1993|month = 8|date = 29}}{{Player3|num = 8|first = Svetozar|last = Popovi\u0107|nat = SER|pos = SG|year = 1987|month = 4|date = 16|m = 1.95}}{{Player3|num = 10|first = Stefan|last = Mati\u0107|pos = SF|nat = SER|m = 2.00|year = 1991|month = 4|date = 5}}{{Player3|num = 11|first = Rado\u0161|last = \u0160e\u0161lija|pos = C|m = 2.08|nat = SER|year = 1992|month = 2|date = 4}}{{Player3|num = 12|first = Aleksandar|last = Bursa\u0107|nat = SER|pos = PF|m = 2.07|year = 1995|month = 3|date = 19}}{{Player3|num = 13|first = Marko|last = Brankovi\u0107|pos = SF|m = 2.00|nat = SER}}{{Player3|num = 15|first = Marko|last = Radonji\u0107|pos = SG|nat = SER|m = 1.91|year = 1993|month = 2|date = 6}}{{Player3|num = 20|first = Marko|last = Jeremi\u0107|pos = SG|m = 1.91|nat = SER|year = 1991|month = 11|date = 23}}{{Player3|num = 45|first = Milo\u0161|last = Grubor|pos = SF|m = 2.01|nat = SER|year = 1991|month = 1|date = 13}}{{Player3|num = -|first = Milo\u0161|last = Radenovi\u0107|nat = SER|pos = PF|m = 1.98|year = 1996|month = 5|date = 7}}{{Player3|num = -|first = \u0110or\u0111e|last = Cvjetan|nat = SER}}\n\n<!-- end list of players -->\n{{Basketball roster footer|head_coach = * {{player||SER|[[Du\u0161an Almipijevi\u0107]]}}}}\n\n=== Depth chart ===\n{{Basketball depth chart|alt_color = Blue|label_color = White|line_color = Red|starter_c = [[Rado\u0161 \u0160e\u0161lija]]|starter_pf = [[Neboj\u0161a Jovi\u0161i\u0107]]|starter_sf = [